                            <comment id="12649403" author="mcculls" created="Thu, 20 Nov 2008 16:44:07 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Yes, the latest development version of Bnd is very different and requires Java5 - so this will be a major version update to the bundleplugin (1.6.0)&lt;br/&gt;
