                            <comment id="12651500" author="rzanner" created="Fri, 28 Nov 2008 08:52:33 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Since I require this fixed rather urgently, I want this to be in the next planned version...&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12652830" author="mcculls" created="Wed, 3 Dec 2008 15:26:13 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Fixed in trunk with the update to Bnd 0.0.295 - however, note that I&apos;m still testing this against various projects to check for any build breaks.&lt;/p&gt;

